#### Example usage:

bash run_ibis.sh [ibis executable] [plink file prefix] [# of cpus]

e.g.,
bash run_ibis.sh ~/ibis/ibis Himba 16 where Himba.[bed][bim][fam] is in the directory and .bim has its genetic map coordinates filled out


bash run_crest.sh [crest directory without trailing forward slash] [genome len in cM] [bim file]

bash run_crest.sh ~/crest 3346.254639 Himba.bim 

#### Himba details

genome_len = 3346.254639
